<div id="content">
    <div class="post_block">
        <h1>Abstract Algorithm</h1>
        <div class="post_info">
            <span class="triangle"></span>
            <span class="hright"></span>
        </div>

        <p>Hello, my name is Dragan Okanovic. I am real-time graphics and front-end programmer from Serbia. And this is my blog website. You can <a href="{CONFIG_WEBSITE}/about">contact</a> me if you want to.</p>

        <h1>Latest entries</h1>
        <div class="post_info">
            <span class="triangle"></span>
            <span class="hright"></span>
        </div>

        <ul>[foreach post in 5|Post::recent]
            <li><a href="post/title/{post.link}">{post.title}</a></li>
        [end]</ul>

        <p>You can view entire <a href="{CONFIG_WEBSITE}/archive">archive</a> of posts or search through them.</p>
    </div>
</div>